Creating Block Design in Vivado

Open Vivado → Create New Project.

Add the exported AES IP into IP Catalog.

Open IP Integrator → Create Block Design.

Add the following blocks:

Zynq Processing System (PS7)

AXI DMA (for high-speed streaming)

AES-128 IP (exported from Vitis HLS)

Connect them:

PS7 → AXI Interconnect → AXI DMA → AES IP.

Ensure AXI4-Lite interface connects for control.

Ensure AXI4-Stream interface connects for input/output data.

Connect clocks and resets.

3. Validate & Implement

Run Validate Design (no errors should appear).

Generate Bitstream.

Export Hardware (XSA) including Bitstream.
